title: #92Noon! Florio/Snob/Hayes/Arif/Pierce
description: Mike Florio opens the show, then Stump the Snob finished the first hour....Dan Hayes and Arif Hasan back to back on Twins and Vikings coverage from the Athletic...then final hour features Vikings DT Michael Pierce addressing the media this morning!
